        <section id="about">
            <h2>About ReSmokle</h2>
            <p>At ReSmokle, we’re on a mission to transform how the vaping and smoking industries think about waste. Born out of a passion for sustainability and a frustration with the growing mountain of single-use packaging, ReSmokle offers a bold new solution: we collect, clean, and recycle used materials—giving them a second life as reusable products or raw materials for 3D printing. From our pipe-cleaning service to our plans for repurposed plastic goods, everything we do is rooted in environmental responsibility, innovation, and community impact. Headquartered in Cincinnati, Ohio, we’re proud to be the first to bring this kind of circular economy solution to our region—one item at a time.</p>
        </section>

